Postsingular

mike

   November 2, 2007

   Rudy Rucker, one of the founders of cyberpunk, has released the
   electronic version of his latest novel, Postsingular, under a CC
   Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivs license.

   Via Boing Boing.
